29
00:02:30,670 --> 00:02:32,810
I think I still

30
00:02:34,540 --> 00:02:36,900
need this counselor-visitor relationship.

31
00:02:38,520 --> 00:02:39,930
Mr. Xiao Mo.

32
00:02:39,930 --> 00:02:44,439
I think you might have something to say but you are not ready yet.

33
00:02:46,910 --> 00:02:48,550
I am not a victim anymore.

34
00:02:48,550 --> 00:02:50,470
Not anymore.

35
00:02:51,240 --> 00:02:53,559
Does the fact that you're no longer a victim make you feel happy?

36
00:02:53,559 --> 00:02:55,570
I am not happy!

37
00:03:00,440 --> 00:03:02,720
I'm sorry, Miss He. Sorry. So sorry.

38
00:03:02,720 --> 00:03:05,540
I'm sorry. I lost control. Sorry.

39
00:03:06,190 --> 00:03:11,470
It's all right. In this place, you can release any of your emotions.

40
00:03:11,470 --> 00:03:12,990
Why?

41
00:03:13,750 --> 00:03:16,909
I really don't know why. They bullied me and isolated me.

42
00:03:16,909 --> 00:03:21,099
I just fought back once. But I still feel as if I was the one who did the wrong thing.

43
00:03:21,099 --> 00:03:24,149
