66
00:04:54,239 --> 00:04:55,510
I hid.

67
00:04:55,510 --> 00:04:57,270
I was a coward, a wuss.

68
00:04:57,270 --> 00:04:58,920
I hid. I hid in a corner.

69
00:04:58,920 --> 00:05:01,269
I could hear their voices. I could hear him twitching.

70
00:05:01,269 --> 00:05:05,269
I knew how much he wished someone could step forward to offer him some help. But no one did.

71
00:05:06,200 --> 00:05:07,729
I didn't.

72
00:05:07,729 --> 00:05:10,709
The reason you hate yourself is you didn't help him back then.

73
00:05:10,709 --> 00:05:14,509
