74
00:05:20,400 --> 00:05:23,230
That's him!

75
00:05:23,230 --> 00:05:25,730
It's him!

76
00:05:28,270 --> 00:05:30,490
What is in your head now?

77
00:05:31,440 --> 00:05:33,270
I would be isolated again.

78
00:05:33,270 --> 00:05:35,370
I would be beaten up again.

79
00:05:35,370 --> 00:05:36,550
What happened?

80
00:05:36,550 --> 00:05:38,350
Because I helped him.

81
00:05:39,660 --> 00:05:41,340
They would target me had I stepped forward to help him.

82
00:05:41,340 --> 00:05:43,480
They would torture me in many ways.

83
00:05:43,480 --> 00:05:46,310
You know, I even thought it was good for me. I was thinking,

84
00:05:46,310 --> 00:05:49,129
they finally went to bully another kid so they wouldn't target me every day.

85
00:05:49,129 --> 00:05:51,250
Now that I think about it, my thoughts were so despicable.

86
00:05:51,250 --> 00:05:54,100
I think I deserve everything bad that's happening to me today.

87
00:05:54,880 --> 00:05:56,110
No.

88
00:05:56,110 --> 00:06:00,559
You didn't protect him because you had to protect yourself first.

89
00:06:04,060 --> 00:06:05,730
Can I really do that?

90
00:06:06,950 --> 00:06:10,689
Can people really protect themselves regardless of other people?

91
00:06:10,689 --> 00:06:12,780
I am not sure.

92
00:06:12,780 --> 00:06:14,670
That sounds so cruel.

93
00:06:14,670 --> 00:06:18,969
