94
00:06:18,969 --> 00:06:23,999
Not only the white ones but also red, green and blue ones.

95
00:06:23,999 --> 00:06:25,300
He tried to spit them out. They didn't let him do that.

96
00:06:25,300 --> 00:06:29,309
They held his mouth and forced him to swallow.

97
00:06:29,309 --> 00:06:31,540
And he did.

98
00:06:31,540 --> 00:06:35,339
They also ground chalks into powder and stuffed into his nose.

99
00:06:35,339 --> 00:06:39,739
They blew the powder into his nose, again and again. They just repeated it.

100
00:06:43,880 --> 00:06:48,100
He was only fourteen years old that year.

