543
00:35:47,089 --> 00:35:49,610
No, absolutely no. You can't be so clingy.

544
00:35:49,610 --> 00:35:53,020
Your hand! You know I'm a neat freak.

545
00:35:54,800 --> 00:35:56,600
Naughty girl.

546
00:35:58,420 --> 00:35:59,850
How are you recently?

547
00:35:59,850 --> 00:36:02,570
Do you still have nightmares?

548
00:36:03,280 --> 00:36:05,140
Well, it's okay.

549
00:36:05,140 --> 00:36:08,120
Mom, how about you go live with me?

550
00:36:08,120 --> 00:36:11,549
