551
00:36:11,549 --> 00:36:12,710
I'll come back to live with you then.

552
00:36:12,710 --> 00:36:14,050
You want to live with me?

553
00:36:14,050 --> 00:36:16,460
No. You won't be able to find a husband.

554
00:36:17,190 --> 00:36:20,420
Did you have a fight with Lili?

555
00:36:20,420 --> 00:36:23,600
No. I just think if I live here and

556
00:36:23,600 --> 00:36:27,899
commute to my office every day, there is a sense of ritual as working.

557
00:36:27,899 --> 00:36:30,100
Don't use some fancy terms to lie to me. What sense of ritual?

558
00:36:30,100 --> 00:36:32,670
You don't even blush when you lie.

559
00:36:33,740 --> 00:36:35,050
Did you two fall out?

560
00:36:35,050 --> 00:36:36,940
No.

561
00:36:38,670 --> 00:36:40,459
Let me tell you this, Dun Dun.

562
00:36:40,459 --> 00:36:44,849
I want to have a good chat with you about some issues and don't think this is useless.

563
00:36:44,849 --> 00:36:48,599
When it's about human hearts and human relations, we old ladies

564
00:36:48,599 --> 00:36:51,719
can talk to you for seven days nonstop and we haven't finished yet.

565
00:36:51,719 --> 00:36:53,080
I just like listening to you talk about these things.

566
00:36:53,080 --> 00:36:55,280
Then let's talk for seven days nonstop!

567
00:36:55,280 --> 00:36:56,630
Really?

568
00:36:56,630 --> 00:36:58,230
Okay.

569
00:37:00,140 --> 00:37:06,059
If you ask me, my silly daughter seems to be very energetic and strong all the time.

570
00:37:06,059 --> 00:37:11,509
But I know well that you have a soft, fragile, and kind heart.

571
00:37:11,509 --> 00:37:15,629
You can easily get obsessed and struggled with things. Right?

572
00:37:16,980 --> 00:37:18,560
Dun Dun, here's the thing.

573
00:37:18,560 --> 00:37:22,390
maybe you think everyone and everything you meet

574
00:37:22,390 --> 00:37:24,630
seems to be just a little part of your life.

575
00:37:24,630 --> 00:37:27,229
So you can deal with them casually by just throwing them away.

576
00:37:27,229 --> 00:37:29,849
You might avoid a problem instead of solving it.

577
00:37:29,849 --> 00:37:32,230
But actually one's life

578
00:37:32,230 --> 00:37:36,699
is made of things happening and people you meet.

579
00:37:36,699 --> 00:37:38,840
All of them form your life.

580
00:37:38,840 --> 00:37:42,719
You can't always avoid and give up when you encounter problems.

581
00:37:42,719 --> 00:37:45,050
What are you left with your life then?

582
00:37:46,080 --> 00:37:47,800
Take Lili for example.

583
00:37:47,800 --> 00:37:50,240
I don't know what conflict you two have.

584
00:37:50,240 --> 00:37:53,479
No matter who is right, I hope you can be the bigger person.

585
00:37:53,479 --> 00:37:56,230
Don't just give up such a good friend.

586
00:37:56,230 --> 00:37:58,430
Face the problem bravely.

587
00:37:58,430 --> 00:38:02,040
You can't solve a problem by pretending it's not there. Did you hear me?

588
00:38:02,040 --> 00:38:04,649
- Um.
- Uh-huh.

589
00:38:04,649 --> 00:38:07,480
