608
00:40:12,840 --> 00:40:15,390
before I left.

609
00:40:15,390 --> 00:40:17,250
I don't know what was wrong with me.

610
00:40:17,250 --> 00:40:19,660
I think I'm so selfish.

611
00:40:20,277 --> 00:40:23,950
She never takes the initiative to express her emotions.

612
00:40:23,950 --> 00:40:26,660
She must be devastating this time.

613
00:40:29,950 --> 00:40:32,689
You know, once our company went for a team building.

614
00:40:32,689 --> 00:40:35,120
