00:41:38,569 --> 00:41:40,870
Maybe it's because you knew her very well.

635
00:41:40,870 --> 00:41:46,170
You knew exactly what she wanted to say or what she was going to say.

636
00:41:46,170 --> 00:41:47,810
You...

637
00:41:48,940 --> 00:41:52,089
